title: Own Your Dreams
itunes:title: Own Your Dreams
description:
Episode 536 - What does it take to bring your dreams into reality? You need to learn how to "own" them in your mind before you own them in the physical world. You need to normalize the feeling of owning what you want. In this episode, I will teach you the secrets of how to do that so that you can create the life that you truly want.
